longBusinessSummary: inTerra Resources Corp., a development stage company, focuses on the acquisition and development of exploration properties in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company was founded in 1998. It was formerly known as China Resources Group, Ltd. and changed its name to inTerra Resources Corp. in November 2006. inTerra Resources is headquartered in Mississauga, Canada.
